snippet.title: Princesses Never Lose! - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Erica, princess of the Tolinia Kingdom, as she fights to unify the Stivale Peninsula against a powerful, modernized country, that threatens to undermine the peninsula's sovereignty.

Princesses Never Lose! will release on March 20 on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1058060/Princesses_Never_Lose/
